.TH "LIGHTNING-RESTORE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-restore \- companion to backup; recovers from a remote
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning restore
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning restore — companion to backup; recovers from a remote.

Implements FEAT-187 §restore.

Usage:
  lightning restore <wallet-remote-url> [<wallet-name>]

Clones the wallet repo, prompts for the seed (FEAT-185
`seed import`), unlocks the daemon, runs the latest SCB.
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
